data.description: Livable great room floor plan with spacious rooms throughout. Downstairs features a huge living room with gas fireplace, kitchen with eating area, and a formal dining room (currently office). Upstairs primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and bath with linen cabinet and dual sinks. Additional bedrooms share a jack-n-jill bath. Private location tucked into the end of the street with large trees, a covered patio, and tool shed. Freshly painted exterior. Room for small boat/trailer, or addl. vehicle parking. Forced air gas heat is supplemented with 4 mini split units for energy efficient heating and cooling. Great location near park, shopping, and easy access to 205. HES = 7 [Home Energy Score = 7. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222972]
